\ CONSTANT — bind a value to a name. Unlike a colon-def that pushes
\ a literal, CONSTANT uses no call/return overhead of its own beyond
\ the usual DOCOL/LIT/EXIT body.
-65280 CONSTANT UART-DATA
-65279 CONSTANT UART-STAT
42     CONSTANT ANSWER
365    CONSTANT YEAR
ANSWER .
YEAR .
UART-DATA .
UART-STAT .
